This is an educational Next.js starter. Keep all code beginner-readable.
Preserve the Five Boxes comments in every file.
The AI provider is configured via env vars. Never hardcode model names or keys.
Mock mode with no AI_API_KEY must always work without errors.
Use shadcn/ui components. Do not introduce other UI libraries.
Use the Vercel AI SDK (ai package). Do not use the raw openai package.
When modifying AI behaviour, only edit SYSTEM_PROMPT in app/api/chat/route.ts.
Keep one-click Vercel deployment working.
